# CircuitSense AI — API Keys
# No .env file needed. API keys are entered by the user in the sidebar UI
# and stored only in their browser's localStorage. No server-side secrets required.

# Supported providers (enter key in the app sidebar):
# Groq (free):         starts with gsk_    → https://console.groq.com/keys
# Google Gemini (free): starts with AIza   → https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
# Anthropic:           starts with sk-ant- → https://console.anthropic.com
# OpenAI:              starts with sk-     → https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
# OpenRouter:          starts with sk-or-  → https://openrouter.ai/keys
